'''亚洲达人秀''' (英语：Asia's Got Talents)是播出'''[[达人秀|达人秀]]'''专营权的区域版本在频道[[AXN|AXN]]。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://variety.com/2014/tv/news/simon-cowells-got-talent-format-extends-to-asia-1201298562/ | title=Simon Cowell’s ‘Got Talent’ Format Extends to Asia | publisher=''Variety'' | date=September 5, 2014 | accessdate=October 21, 2014 | author=Frater, Patrick | archive-date=2016-03-05 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305052836/http://variety.com/2014/tv/news/simon-cowells-got-talent-format-extends-to-asia-1201298562/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>胜利者可在达人秀获得总值奖金100,000美元。<ref>{{cite news|title=Search for first 'Asia's Got Talent' winner starts March|url=http://www.philstar.com/entertainment/2015/03/06/1430722/search-first-asias-got-talent-winner-starts-march|accessdate=14 March 2015|publisher=''[[The_Philippine_Star|The Philippine Star]]''|date=6 March 2015|location=Manila|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924191235/http://www.philstar.com/entertainment/2015/03/06/1430722/search-first-asias-got-talent-winner-starts-march|dead-url=no}}</ref> 亚洲达人秀开始于2015年3月12日,参赛者包括20个[[亚洲|亚洲]]国家,<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.philstar.com/entertainment/2014/09/20/1371235/axn-bringing-asias-got-talent | title=AXN bringing in 'Asia's Got Talent' | publisher=''[[The_Philippine_Star|The Philippine Star]]'' | date=September 20, 2014 | accessdate=October 21, 2014 | archive-date=2015-09-24 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924185719/http://www.philstar.com/entertainment/2014/09/20/1371235/axn-bringing-asias-got-talent | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="ABS 1">{{cite web | url=http://www.abs-cbnnews.com/entertainment/01/23/15/marc-rovilson-host-asias-got-talent | title=Marc, Rovilson to host 'Asia's Got Talent' | publisher=''[[ABS-CBN_News|ABS-CBN News]]'' | date=January 23, 2015 | accessdate=January 24, 2015 | archive-date=2015-07-07 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150707184035/http://www.abs-cbnnews.com/entertainment/01/23/15/marc-rovilson-host-asias-got-talent | dead-url=no }}</ref>最终播出九周后于2015年5月14日的总决赛结束。

节目主持人为Marc Nelson与Rovilson Fernandez，评委由二人构成，<ref name="ABS 1"/> 第一季评委由印尼的[[安谷|安谷]]、音乐家[[大卫·沃尔特·福斯特|大卫·沃尔特·福斯特]]、英国[[辣妹合唱團|辣妹合唱團]]成員Malanie C与台湾艺人[[吴建豪|吴建豪]]四人来担任。第二季評委則由[[安谷|安谷]]、[[大卫·沃尔特·福斯特|大卫·沃尔特·福斯特]]續任，同時加入韓國[[朴宰範|朴宰範]].

